# apps
### Get all apps
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps

### Create an app
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Mac Pro"
}

### Get app by token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps/213776

### Update app by token
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps/213776
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated xx"
}

