# chats

### Get all chats for an application
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps/213776/chats

### Get a specific chat for an application
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps/213776/chats/1

### Create a chat for an application
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps/839104685/chats
Content-Type: application/json

#################################################
# messages

### Get all messages for a chat
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps/839104685/chats/63/messages

### Get a specific message for a chat
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps/839104685/chats/63/messages/1000

### Create a message for a chat
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/apps/839104685/chats/63/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": {
        "content": "Hello, world!"
    }
}

